<h2>Welcome To Telkom+</h2>
<br><br><br><br>
<p>Telkom+ is the new way to automate home appliances. The application has the best usability and controllability for devices. The user-friendly application is accompanied by the company&aposs adaptable device that bridges the gap from &quotnon-smart&quot devices and already connectable smart devices towards a unified application that has the ability to control the smallest detail of a device to the most crucial aspects of a device. Telkom+ intends to give complete freedom of control to users over their devices and its capabilities.</p> 



